Before releasing, please do the following:

- Set the correct name of the directory
mv iNZightVIT-RELEASE iNZightVIT-2.0.0

- Copy the following directories/files outside of the current directory:

cd iNZightVIT-2.0.0
mkdir ../inz-tmp
mv .git/ ../inz-tmp
mv README.md ../inz-tmp
mv READ_BEFORE_RELEASE ../inz-tmp

- convert to .zip file
cd ..
zip -r iNZightVIT-2.0.0 iNZightVIT-RELEASE

- restore the files
cd iNZightVIT-2.0.0
mv -r ../inz-tmp/* ./
rm -r ../inz-tmp

cd ..
mv iNZightVIT-2.0.0 iNZightVIT-RELEASE
